# ViralRefer Premium — Environment Variables (TEMPLATE ONLY)
# ========================================================================
# SECURITY: NEVER commit real secrets to git. This file contains ONLY
# placeholders. Copy to .env.local (or .env) and replace values.
#
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#   # Edit .env.local with YOUR keys from Supabase dashboard.
#
# Vite automatically exposes ONLY vars prefixed VITE_ to client code via
# import.meta.env at build/dev time. Non-VITE_ (e.g. service role) are
# server-only (Edge Functions use Deno.env.get or hosting secrets).
#
# REQUIRED:
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL       - Your Supabase project URL (e.g. https://xxx.supabase.co)
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  - Your project's anon/public key (JWT)
#
# RECOMMENDED:
#   VITE_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY      - Cloudflare Turnstile site key for bot protection
#   (no VITE_ADMIN_PASSWORD)    - Admin login uses edge verify_owner_password + ADMIN_OWNER_PASSWORD on Supabase only
#
# NEVER put real keys here. .gitignore excludes .env*, .env.local, etc.
# ========================================================================

# Supabase (required) — REPLACE WITH YOUR VALUES
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.YOUR_ANON_KEY_HERE...

# Cloudflare Turnstile (CAPTCHA) — get free keys at dash.cloudflare.com/turnstile
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY=0x4AAAAA_YOUR_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY_HERE...

# Admin Edge Function secret — SERVER ONLY (Supabase secrets + local scripts; never VITE_)
# ADMIN_ACTION_SECRET=your-admin-action-secret-here
# ADMIN_OWNER_PASSWORD=your-owner-admin-password

# Referral marketing automation (scripts/post-growth-queue.mjs — local .env.local only)
# GROWTH_POST_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC...     # optional; falls back to FUNNEL_NOTIFY_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
# GROWTH_POST_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=@viralrefer         # public channel https://t.me/viralrefer
# X_API_KEY=...                                    # optional — full auto-post to @viralrefer
# X_API_SECRET=...
# X_ACCESS_TOKEN=...
# X_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET=...

# Off-site funnel alerts (Supabase Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets, NOT Vite)
# Preferred — Telegram Bot API (messages your phone even when admin is closed):
# FUNNEL_NOTIFY_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=123456:ABC-DEF...   # from @BotFather
# FUNNEL_NOTIFY_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789              # your user id or group id
# Optional fallback webhook if Telegram secrets are not set:
# FUNNEL_NOTIFY_WEBHOOK_URL=https://ntfy.sh/your-topic
# FUNNEL_NOTIFY_IMPORTANT_ONLY=true   # optional — default alerts ALL funnel steps

# Google Search Console site verification (optional — paste meta content value from GSC)
# VITE_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=your-verification-token-here

# Optional (for local Edge function testing only; NEVER commit real value)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...YOUR_SERVICE_ROLE_HERE...

# Deployment (examples — set in your hosting dashboard, not here)
# CF_PAGES=1
# VERCEL=1

# Admin test password for E2E / local scripts (set in shell/CI; not bundled in client)
# ADMIN_TEST_PASSWORD=your-strong-test-pass-here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# SECRET ROTATION & SCANNING NOTES (Sentinel Key Purge):
# - Rotate Supabase anon/service_role keys in Supabase Dashboard > API if
#   ever suspected compromised. Update hosting envs + redeploy immediately.
# - Rotate Turnstile secrets in Cloudflare + update VITE_TURNSTILE_SITEKEY.
# - Rotate ADMIN_OWNER_PASSWORD on Supabase edge regularly.
# - Run secret scans in CI: recommend gitleaks, trufflehog, or GitHub secret
#   scanning. Never allow PRs with new keys.
# - After any rotation: rebuild, clear caches, test E2E with new ADMIN_TEST_PASSWORD.
# - See README.md and ADMIN_GUIDE.md "Rotating Keys & Secrets".
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
